          <En>The activity of buying goods or services, typically from stores or online.</En>
          <Example>I went shopping for new clothes at the mall.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="253cf7f5-a7fa-4561-8e9b-6a02d34694d0">
              <Vi>Mua đồ dùng, quần áo, thực phẩm… tại siêu thị, chợ, hoặc online.</Vi>
              <En>Browsing and purchasing items such as groceries, clothing, or electronics.</En>
            </Situation>
          </Situations>
        </Meaning>
        <Meaning id="8a0ffaa3-f8ce-4632-a669-24b8d0f607c7" type="Verb">
          <Vi>Mua sắm (động từ)</Vi>
          <En>To visit stores or markets to buy goods.</En>
          <Example>She likes to shop on weekends.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="c4015d02-07a1-4ec3-baa2-c03079251445">
